{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-19", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "狂人的誓言", "storyInfo": "遠北事件結束之後，阿洛伊澤在和維特議長回顧事件時，對他隱瞞了自己已經向羅德島透露了石棺線索的事實。礦脈枯竭的消息擴散開來，仍在持續影響著烏薩斯各地。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_act15main_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_sanatorium_dining", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>聖駿堡榮軍院</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……以上就是遠北事件的經過。我會在一週內整理並提交書面報告。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦你了，中尉，但我還有一些疑問。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的這些——深入礦區、追查礦工、掩護他們在集團軍的炮火下逃離……似乎都只是事件的過程。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生命有播種、生長、收穫，事件有起因、經過、結果，缺一不可。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請原諒我的措辭不當，議長閣下，但事件起因和後續處理我剛才都已提及。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些都是分散的資訊。你如實敘述細枝末節，卻沒有看見樹木的完整形貌，而如果連你這個敘述者都不能察覺……閱覽者又如何得知？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道走出軍事學院短短五年，就已經讓你徹底遺忘了文書寫作的規矩？又或者，你想要我向陛下呈上一份殘缺不全的報告？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，我尚能原諒你那些由年輕致使的過錯，烏薩斯卻不再等得起了。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，之後我會在報告裡補齊其他的部分——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是沒有留出足夠時間彌補疏漏導致的後果。試錯的成本太過高昂，得到的經驗與付出的教訓已不成正比。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要你現在就告訴我，你認為葉莉莎女大公在其中扮演了怎樣的角色？她與集團軍的沆瀣一氣是否早有端倪？我們營救的那些倖存者……", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又能否成為我們真正的助力？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不確定我現在是否已經掌握了足夠的資訊可以談論……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#10$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是親歷者，沒有人比你更有資格談論。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，孩子。無論你說什麼，我都會傾聽。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我認為女大公在一開始就只是順水推舟。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們計劃進入礦區前，她就已經知曉內衛死亡、礦工逃跑等事件的發生。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此她只需從指縫中洩露一點消息，蟄伏已久的第四集團軍就有理由在“清理門戶”的同時，順理成章地以剿滅叛亂為由向中央區進發。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣，女大公就能掩蓋有內衛死在自己轄區一事，集團軍也能如願部署兵力在中央區邊界……就像現在。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於集團軍陳兵在中央區邊界的目的，想必您比任何人都清楚。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們將陛下的仁慈誤認為是懦弱，他們會付出應有的代價。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿洛達，我親愛的中尉。我贊同你大部分的推測，但你仍然遺漏了一點——聖愚。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後它消失了，我無從確證它真實與否，甚至我也看不到深究它的必要，畢竟……我們都曾親眼目睹上一任聖愚在火中消亡。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不認為出現在遠北的那個是聖愚？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是認為您理應比我知曉更多。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令人憂心的狂人……舊時代的遺毒。我會調查清楚的，畢竟，烏薩斯早已不再需要聖愚。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，讓我們回到先前的話題吧。告訴我，中尉，他們的目的算是達成了嗎？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少他們沒能阻止礦脈枯竭的消息外洩，這也指向您剛才的另一個問題——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們營救的那些倖存者能否真正成為助力？事實上，他們已經幫忙了。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰面上的火帶，幾乎喚醒了涅瓦湖靠近聖駿堡方向上的所有崗哨；礦工送出的消息，幾乎傳遍了整個烏薩斯。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“烏薩斯拋棄了他們！下一群被拋棄的人是誰？”一時之間，幾乎所有人都在這樣問。報紙上、城際通訊中、深夜電台裡……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦區裡的礦工這樣問，城市裡的工人也這樣問；富裕的市民這樣問，貧困的流浪者也這樣問；軍人這樣問，學生也這樣問。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女大公以為那些礦工都會死在遠北，但他們活了下來。他們不僅印證了礦脈枯竭的消息，也揭開了改良政策弊端的一角——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是改良，只是緩慢的、循序漸進的改善，已經無法滿足如今烏薩斯發展的迫切需求了。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在更多人被迫成為驅動烏薩斯這台龐大機器的燃料之前，我們必須有所作為。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您剛才也說，烏薩斯不再等得起……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中尉，我想你有一點離題了。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得，你說過那則訊息是羅德島幫助感染者礦工發送出去的。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，沒錯，但我們現在更應該注意的是——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對羅德島有什麼看法？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是值得警惕的對象。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在追蹤和撤離過程中都展現出軍事行動等級的紀律與能力，加上他們對感染者的瞭解有著先天優勢，這些都值得我們警惕。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，這份值得警惕的力量也可以為我們所用。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我所知，羅德島目前在烏薩斯境內還沒能設立固定的辦事處，也許我們可以邀請他們在聖駿堡或者周邊城市……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女大公可能會搶先。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是急躁的人。你是否曾對羅德島的人提起過“凱爾希”這個名字？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。他們的領導人說，雖然凱爾希的確曾作為醫生活躍在羅德島，但如今已經因為一場意外死去。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確鑿無疑？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經派人前往事發地點查證，現階段可暫且認為確鑿無疑。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯中央區，荒野</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……凱爾希已經死了。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維特議長從切城研究所檔案裡拾起的名字，現在已經不再具有效用。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你們在尋找凱爾希。;為什麼？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line125", "option2": "line125"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然是因為石棺。烏薩斯需要石棺內蘊含的能源。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你知道石棺現在在哪裡？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line132"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，我並不清楚詳細的情況。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但維特告訴了你凱爾希這個名字。;他希望你透過我們，找到凱爾希。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line138", "option2": "line138"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "維特信任你。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line140"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，否則他也不會只派我——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只派我去遠北。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，他信任我。說實在的，軍人的天職是服從命令，即使他派我來遠北，讓我命喪於此，我也毫無怨言。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不該是這樣。礦工和平民遭到屠殺，女大公卻全身而退，集團軍甚至得以陳兵聖駿堡城外。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#9$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果不該是這樣！如今，我又有什麼臉回去……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#9$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "戈爾奇科娃中尉。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line152"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "如果我告訴你，凱爾希還有復活的可能……;你會怎麼做？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line154", "option2": "line154"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在開玩笑？這有可能嗎？！難道這個凱爾希也是某種傳說中的精怪，能夠無數次死而復活？", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，不對。議長好像的確說過……秘密警察曾經認為，作為所長的凱爾希已經死在了那次變故當中。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就這樣告訴我了？難道是指望我因此對你們抱有同等的信任嗎？你們甚至都不是烏薩斯人——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那如果曾經是烏薩斯人呢？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使你真的什麼也不知道，我們也不會遺忘，你曾在那裡與我們並肩幫助感染者撤離。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們感謝你的付出，戈爾奇科娃中尉，即使你並不需要這份感謝，對嗎？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我吧，而我將重新作為一個烏薩斯人去聆聽。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#7$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我早該知道我拒絕不了去喚起一個流亡者對烏薩斯的認同。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，關於石棺，我所知道的也十分有限……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_sanatorium_dining", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——中尉？", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，請問您剛才說什麼？", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼。我的壞習慣又開始了，一跟你們這樣的年輕人談論起“國家”、“明天”、“未來”，我就停不下來……", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#6$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你是真的太累了，需要休息，我已佔用你太多時間了。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，議長閣下，我只是在思考您剛才說的——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#3$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先去休息吧，中尉。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與遠北不同，這個時節的聖駿堡至少還有少許白晝。只是等你回過神來，別遺忘了這份尚未完成的報告。", "name": "維特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1984_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadcast_third", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$faceoff_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“在北原重啟部分先前關閉的礦場之後，第三集團軍將視線轉向中部地區。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“日前，第四集團軍仍違法滯留在中央區邊界，在此敬告市民，請勿私自穿越崗哨防線，前往涅瓦湖水域。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“第一集團軍越過帝國議會，對中部數十所大學進行懲罰性的強制徵兵，全國多地學生的聲援抗議遭血腥鎮壓。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“第二、第七集團軍應聖駿堡的要求，已動員前往……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報紙上全都是這種消息。我有一個表妹在中部那邊上學，我已經很久沒聽到她的近況了。", "name": "學生A"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽說了嗎？卡謝娜老師不是被調去聖駿堡國立大學，而是去礦區，去教那些礦工識字了！", "name": "學生B"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，最勇敢最無私的人也不過如此。等我畢業以後，我也想追隨卡謝娜老師的腳步……", "name": "學生B"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真希望還能再見到她。", "name": "學生B"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你們不要太相信這些報紙！上面只有壞消息，都是為了製造焦慮、打壓我們的信心。", "name": "學生C"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下在伊戈爾紀念公園裡有一個學生會發起的抗議活動，你們要去嗎？", "name": "學生C"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然要去啊！", "name": "學生B"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我也要去！", "name": "學生A"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g13_smallroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_197_poca_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍方的動作很頻繁，各地都有罷工罷課的情況發生，只是鎮壓行動也比以往更加迅速和猛烈……", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且最近，聖駿堡警方好像逮捕了一個闖入帝國議會大廳塗鴉示威的文學系學生，聽說彼得拉設夫斯基小組正在發起募捐，並且策劃營救行動。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是真的，我已經跟他們確認過了。幾乎每家地下小報都在傳播那個人的事蹟，以及他在議會牆上寫的那段話。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "書報審查機構的動作比地下小報的印刷速度慢了太多。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_197_poca_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這次寄給索尼婭的信裡就寫這些吧。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "char_197_poca_1#4"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_197_poca_1#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，她們應該正在返回聖駿堡……", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "char_197_poca_1#3"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是寫一下吧，現在各地都有程度不同的戒嚴，她們不一定能準時趕回聖駿堡。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_197_poca_1#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……希望她們的行動順利。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "char_197_poca_1#3"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定會的。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混進來好像也沒那麼困難。", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我已經幫你入侵監控系統，你也別放鬆警惕。現在說是無限期休會，其實是隨時都有可能再次召開會議。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以連接議會大廳的走廊保持了每小時四次的巡邏頻率，扣掉撤離所需的時間，你還有八分鐘可以在這裡留下一點痕跡。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨地大小便？破壞？敲一塊桌角帶走？", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你能不能做一點動靜小而且有意義的事？", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個嘛……我想一下。", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說回來，我為什麼要穿成這樣進來啊？我覺得我平常穿得也不顯眼啊。", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你穿的是聖駿堡管道維修工人的制服。他們雖然在議會中沒有席位，但常常出入議會大廳，畢竟大廈內各處的維護都需要依靠工人們的辛勤勞動。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們這些學生……則沒有任何身分，也沒有任何得到許可進入議會的可能，更不用說在裡面真正擁有一席之地了。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，我跟你說這些做什麼。我要掛了，記住，你還有六分鐘。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯塔尼結束。", "name": "耳機裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真是個呆子。", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做點什麼比較好呢？六分鐘……", "name": "工人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿著工人制服的學生望向議會大廳中央。代表烏薩斯神聖榮光的徽記正在那面牆上熠熠生輝。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "思索半晌，他眯起眼睛，從工具包裡翻出一罐紅色噴漆。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spryngjy", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布里金今天其實沒有值班，但他鄰居也是他的同事，對方請小兒子來敲響他的門，說自己發燒、頭痛，總之完全沒辦法下床。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出於好心，他幫忙代班了，卻沒想到一走進議會大廳就看到這幅荒唐的景象——"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_groceriespaper", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ceramicrack", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——陛下在上——", "name": "清潔工"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大廳牆壁上，金色的徽記已經完全被凌亂的紅色掩蓋。在那下方，有人用同樣的紅色，留下了烏薩斯語寫就的詞句——"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<color=#FF4200>“勝者為炫耀而據有敗者的徽記，如若我們不能將它擯棄，勝者將永遠為敗者的陰影所籠罩。”</color>", "x": 300.0, "y": 280.0, "alignment": "center", "duration": 1.0, "size": 26.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "multi": "true", "text": "<color=#FF4200>——雅科夫·彼得洛夫，1076年秋於獄中</color>", "x": 500.0, "y": 380.0, "alignment": "center", "duration": 1.0, "size": 26.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "theater", "attributes": {"mode": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ep16", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}